15
00:02:42,541 --> 00:02:45,500
Well, it was a
pretty major storm.

16
00:02:46,416 --> 00:02:49,458
That may be it. The storm could
be the reason IRUO's needed

17
00:02:49,541 --> 00:02:51,208
