That's why master made
Airi like this, so she could

47
00:04:42,833 --> 00:04:45,791
learn a little about
the big, wide world.

48
00:04:45,875 --> 00:04:49,083
Hey. Pay attention, will ya?
There's only one flag left

49
00:04:49,166 --> 00:04:51,500
for the sixth Kimijima
report. "Go to the beach

50
00:04:51,583 --> 00:04:53,666
and surf a wave for
three or more seconds."

51
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:56,375
That's the last thing
I hafta do to unlock it.

52
00:04:56,458 --> 00:04:58,750
The weather forecast
for today, December 12th,

53
00:04:58,833 --> 00:05:00,791
through tomorrow,
December 13th.

54
