Those living in the
Tanegashima region can

55
00:05:03,375 --> 00:05:06,375
expect clear,
cloudless skies. On the--

56
00:05:09,541 --> 00:05:13,500
What the. She's glitching
up now? Not Airi, too.

57
00:05:36,875 --> 00:05:38,833
Okay, Mom, I'm back now.

58
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:41,958
