the ocean again. You
must be really passionate

65
00:05:59,083 --> 00:06:01,708
about this gig as
Yashio's surfing coach, huh?

66
00:06:01,791 --> 00:06:04,500
I don't think passionate's
the right way to put it.

67
00:06:04,583 --> 00:06:06,750
I dunno. I guess I just...

68
00:06:14,958 --> 00:06:16,458
Epic surfer fail, huh?

69
00:06:17,041 --> 00:06:19,333
If you're gonna be
like that, I'm hanging up.

70
00:06:19,416 --> 00:06:21,583
H-Have you seen
the IRUO notice?

71
00:06:21,666 --> 00:06:23,583
Why? Something going on?

72
00:06:23,666 --> 00:06:27,041
Th-They're doing extensive
maintenance. On the 24th.

73
00:06:27,125 --> 00:06:28,833
It just had to be
right around Christmas.

74
00:06:28,916 --> 00:06:31,625
When all the real-lifers come
crawling out of the woodwork.

75
00:06:32,458 --> 00:06:34,583
What about people like me?
What about the shut-ins who

76
00:06:34,666 --> 00:06:37,250
wanna see the world from the
comfort of their own homes?

77
00:06:37,333 --> 00:06:40,333
That's tragic, but I don't
get what it has to do with me.

78
00:06:40,416 --> 00:06:42,500
Well, there's always a chance
they'll do a server reset

79
