84
00:06:59,083 --> 00:07:01,083
What about never getting
to talk to Airi anymore?

85
00:07:01,166 --> 00:07:04,333
Talk about an epic sadface.
Although, if I had to choose,

86
00:07:04,416 --> 00:07:06,708
I would pick Gezi
over Airi, so many more

87
