depraved conversation!

88
00:07:09,875 --> 00:07:14,083
Snow, snow, snow! Snow
is falling, falling down.

89
00:07:14,166 --> 00:07:15,833
Snow is falling,
hit the ground!

90
00:07:15,916 --> 00:07:16,916
Aw, loli-girl!

91
00:07:18,583 --> 00:07:21,041
Oh, yeah. That reminds me,
Akiho said she wants to

92
00:07:21,125 --> 00:07:23,375
