party. And, uh.

93
00:07:23,458 --> 00:07:25,291
She wanted to
invite Airi, too.

94
00:07:25,375 --> 00:07:27,416
A C-Christmas party?
Like, IRL?

95
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:29,875
She was also very
enthusiastic about

96
00:07:29,958 --> 00:07:32,166
the idea of
exchanging presents.

97
00:07:32,250 --> 00:07:34,583
Ooh, Christmas
presents? Really?

98
00:07:34,666 --> 00:07:36,791
I have lots of erotic
novels. You can have as many

99
00:07:36,875 --> 00:07:39,791
as you want, my
lovely little loli! w00t!

100
00:07:39,875 --> 00:07:42,708
The only present Airi wants
is snow! It would be like

101
00:07:42,791 --> 00:07:45,500
a dream come true if there
was snow on Christmas Eve!

102
00:07:45,583 --> 00:07:48,166
You see, that's what Airi
wishes for every year,

103
00:07:48,250 --> 00:07:51,458
